shot! slower delivery, Vincent chips down
        the track, gets well inside the line and bludgeons it over the
        long-off fence - amazing
on the middle and off stump line, defended towards cover
short of a good length delivery on the middle and off stump line, defended with a straight bat and the ball rolls away towards cover
tight delivery on the middle and leg stump line, defended down on the leg side
sharp bouncer and Fleming gets hit on the shoulder while trying to duck under it
driven away square on the off side
short of a good length delivery on the middle and off stump line, defended towards cover
short of a good length delivery on the stumps, Astle leans back and pulls it away to the vacant fine leg fence
quicker delivery outside the off stump, no shot offered
short of a good length delivery outside the off stump, no shot offered
bit of width outside the off stump, cut away to third man for a single
